=-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------=
=                                             REPOS                                             =
=-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------=
CZDS -  The download speed for zone files via the ICANN official website is limited and sometimes
lead to a complete stop of the operation before finishing. Downloading via the terminal, provides
a more secure way to ensure that you download will be sucessfull. I also implemented a simple way
to search for domains on a given zone. Its a simple tool that get its job done.

TAMPERMONKEY - Tampermonkey is a browser extension that let you run JS scripts on a wanted wesite
I'm currently using it to extract domain names from expireddomains.net,  but I believe there will
be more usecases for it in the near future.
